        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "LABOUR: PARTS+LABOUR"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "With a cast of five&nbsp;performers, co-choreographers Emily Gualtieri and David Albert-Toth&rsquo;s new work LABOUR delves into the often-overlooked labour of care that womxn have carried throughout history, bringing it to the forefront through the body, highly physical choreography, and visual storytelling."
      }
    ],
