        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Va falloir toujours toujours: Dance theatre"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Two dance pros and an (unexpected) third contestant are ready to take on the challenge of becoming the PERFECT family! But in this game, are we allowed to fumble? This sparkling pop-philosophy show wreaks havoc with our perfectionist ideals, sparking dishwasher confessions and thoughts about togetherness."
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@value": "https://nac-cna.ca/en/event/38341"
      }
    ],
